{"id": "1499948957248393326", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "392685897637691392", "author_name": "popo006", "author_bot": false, "content": "たしかに言われてみれば対して変わらないかもですね！ハムリンと血へロ気に入ってるのでこのままの垢でサルバ等PU来た時に頑張って引いていきます！ありがとうです(*^^)v", "timestamp": "2026-05-02T01:41:39.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-02T01:43:09.757000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
